      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s configuration, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the finish shows minor stone chipping consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical vitals are top-tier, offering a visceral, naturally aspirated driving experience.",
